comment_data.body:
Could you upgrade to the latest Flutter plugin and let us know if the problem still occurs? That's currently version 69.

If it does still happen, could you append the content of the `*_android.iml` file? It may be in the `android` directory.

Without additional information we're not able to resolve this issue, so it will be closed at this time. You're still free to add more info and respond to any questions above, though. We'll reopen the case if you do. Thanks for your contribution!
